&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>永恒之战</title><link>/p/forever-war/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/p/forever-war/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/p/forever-war/cover.png" alt="Featured image of post 永恒之战" />&lt;h1 id="永恒之战">
&lt;a href="#%e6%b0%b8%e6%81%92%e4%b9%8b%e6%88%98">#&lt;/a>
&lt;strong>《永恒之战》&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h1>&lt;h2 id="verse-1">
&lt;a href="#verse-1">#&lt;/a>
&lt;strong>Verse 1&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在天空的边缘，太阳升起
燃烧着烈焰，照亮黑暗的宇宙
